<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286593>
    dc:description "FIGURES 64 – 65. 64. Map showing the distribution of B. impetuosus s. l. in North China with records as black spots, the province boundaries in dark grey, and all sites with records of all bumblebee species in light grey. 65. B. impetuosus s. l. worker visiting Saussurea stella (Asteraceae) in Gansu (PW)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286593/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.286612>
    dc:description "FIGURES 104 – 105. 104. Map showing the distribution of B. lepidus in North China with record as black spot, the province boundaries in dark grey, and all sites with records of all bumblebee species in light grey. 105. B. lepidus worker visiting Aconitum gymnandrum (Ranunculaceae) in Gansu." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/286612/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

